---
title: Sidecar
tags: cocktails
servings: 1
---

Coat the rim of a #coupe glass{} with @sugar{} if desired, and set aside.

Add @cognac{1 1/2%oz}, @orange liqueur{3/4%oz} (such as Cointreau), and @lemon juice{3/4%oz} (freshly squeezed) to a shaker with ice and shake until well-chilled, ~{15%seconds}.

Strain into the prepared glass. Garnish with an @orange twist{}.
